# frontend/components/epilogue.tsx: epilogue keep/destroy voting UI

## Context
After the game ends, 1000 Blank White Cards runs an epilogue where players vote to keep or destroy each card created this session. Kept cards enter the permanent RAG corpus. The server sends `{ type: "epilogue", cards: [...] }`. Each player votes `keep` or `destroy` on each card. This component renders the voting UI and sends `epilogue_vote` messages. This replaces the `EpilogueView` stub in `app/room/[code]/page.tsx`.

