# frontend/components/blank-draw-prompt.tsx: blank-draw create-on-the-spot UI

## Context
In 1000 Blank White Cards, drawing a blank card forces the active player to create a new card on the spot before play can continue. When the server sends a `state` with the drawn card having `verdict === "blank"` (or a dedicated `blank_draw` state signal), the active player sees an inline prompt to fill in the card's title and description immediately. This is different from the setup phase ŌĆö it's an interruption during play.

