## Context
The landing page is the first thing a player sees. It has two actions: "Create Room" (calls `POST /rooms`, then redirects to `/room/{code}`) and "Join Room" (takes a code input, calls `POST /rooms/{code}/join` with a name, stores the `player_id` in `localStorage`, then redirects). This is a simple client-side React page ŌĆö no server components needed.

## Files
